{
  "stem": "13079.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Mauthausen was a Class III, otherwise known as an extermination center.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And extermination centers were those that had gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Dachau's gas chamber didn't go in operation until the late '43, or '44.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Mauthausen they leased-- and by the way, when I say leased, Eigruber was the Gauleiter at the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he leased Castle [INAUDIBLE] to the-- the [INAUDIBLE] department of concentration camp use.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they took out the basement and made that into a gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's at Mauthausen, as its base of operations so far as extermination [? at ?] Mauthausen was concerned.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Class IV was also a waste.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that-- I'm not so sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I think Buchenwald was in a Class IV.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Frankly, all of them were such skunks that it was a poor choice between [? riding that horse. ?] But they had quite a impressive group of individuals there in prison.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] some French generals-- officers-- that were there that were executed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Blum, I think, was there, the Frenchman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Leon Blum.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I forgot now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who is the head of Austria at the time of the Anschluss?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm getting too old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But anyway, he and his wife were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had-- well, in Dachau, we had Leopold, Frederick Leopold, Prince of Prussia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was there, a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And who was the preacher?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Niemoller, Pastor Niemoller was at Dachau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the-- what the krauts did, they'd overun the countries, they would take those individuals who either politically or financially were important, and who could say there's a nucleus for opposition.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they [? backed them-- ?] packed them up and sent them off to these camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
